ive%20leaf%20blower%20should%20be%20straightforward%20and%20convenient%20to%20start%2C%20operate%2C%20and%20control.%20I%20paid%20special%20attention%20to%20the%20layout%20and%20design%20of%20the%20controls%2C%20including%20power%20boost%20and%20cruise%20control%20features%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20shape%20and%20design%20of%20the%20carrying%20handle.%20I%20also%20researched%20user%20reviews%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20weren't%20frequent%20complaints%20about%20the%20unit%20being%20complicated%20or%20frustrating%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Even%20an%20extra%20pound%20or%20two%20can%20make%20a%20real%20difference%20in%20how%20comfortable%20your%20blower%20is%20to%20operate.%20If%20blower%20models%20in%20the%20same%20category%20were%20a%20fairly%20close%20match-up%20in%20terms%20of%20power%20and%20usability%2C%20I%20tended%20to%20choose%20the%20lighter%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20top%20picks%20compared%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%20border%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3ECriteria%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EToro%2051621%20UltraPlus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EToro%2051624%20PowerJet%20F700%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EGreenworks%202400702%2024V%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EEgo%20Power%2B%20LB6504%20Cordless%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EHusqvarna%20150BT%20Gas%20Backpack%20Blower%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3ENoise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E68%20dB(A)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E70%20dB(A)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E65%20dB(A)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E65%20dB(A)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E72%20dB(A)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%20(1%20easy%20to%203%20more%20difficult)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E1%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E1%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E3%20(short%20run%20time)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E2%20(heavier%20than%20other%20blowers)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E3%20(more