investing%20on%20his%20blog%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22c72a407801840e8671147560398d78db%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2240%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.liveoffdividends.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELive%20Off%20Dividends%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20are%20three%20big%20lessons%20he%20learned%20from%20his%20parents%20that%20helped%20him%20save%20enough%20to%20get%20started%20as%20a%20landlord.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20He%20learned%20about%20delayed%20gratification%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20important%20things%20O'Reilly%20learned%20from%20his%20family%20was%20the%20idea%20of%20delayed%20gratification.%20As%20a%20kid%2C%20he%20didn't%20always%20get%20what%20he%20wanted%20right%20away.%20It%20didn't%20mean%20he%20couldn't%20have%20it%2C%20he%20just%20had%20to%20put%20in%20the%20time%20and%20effort%20to%20earn%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20wanted%20a%20new%20video%20game%20or%20toy%2C%20I%20would%20ask%20my%20parents%20to%20buy%20it%20for%20me.%20Of%20course%2C%20sometimes%20they%20would%20oblige%20and%20buy%20it%20for%20me.%20Other%20times%2C%20instead%20of%20just%20buying%20the%20game%20for%20me%2C%20they%20would%20give%20me%20things%20to%20do%20around%20the%20house%20to%20earn%20money.%20These%20things%20included%20washing%20their%20cars%2C%20cleaning%2C%20mowing%20the%20lawn%2C%20raking%20leaves%2C%20shoveling%20snow%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Reilly%20told%20Businss%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BEventually%2C%20I%20stopped%20asking%20them%20to%20buy%20me%20things%20and%20rather%20asked%20for%20tasks%20to%20earn%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20by%20the%20time%20he%20completed%20his%20chores%20and%20was%20able%20to%20afford%20the%20original%20item%20he%20wanted%2C%20it%20became%20less%20appealing%20after%20he%20realized%20how%20much%20hard%20work%20had%20to%20go%20into%20earning%20it.%20This%20mindset%20helped%