prosecutor.%20%26quot%3BEither%20one%20of%20them%20could%20be%20viewed%20as%20being%20too%20aggressive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20reassured%20the%20crowd.%20I%20quickly%20got%20bored%20and%20elbowed%20my%20way%20back%20out%20of%20the%20miniature%20media%20mosh%20pit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Burgum%20taking%20questions%20ahead%20of%20the%20debate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e1e42bcfb7f307e5709d21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBurgum%20taking%20questions%20ahead%20of%20the%20debate.%3Cp%3EBryan%20Dozier%2FVariety%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20it's%20really%20like%20to%20be%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bspin%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20anachronistic%20institution%20that%20%E2%80%94%20aside%20from%202020%2C%20for%20obvious%2C%20COVID-related%20reasons%20%E2%80%94%20has%20existed%20as%20a%20parasitic%20outgrowth%20of%20America's%20quadrennial%20presidential%20debates%20since%20Ronald%20Reagan's%201984%20reelection%20campaign.%20Each%20campaign%20trots%20out%20a%20variety%20of%20surrogates%2C%20the%20bulk%20of%20which%20are%20high-profile%20governors%20and%20members%20of%20Congress%2C%20to%20proffer%20talking%20points%20to%20reporters%20before%20and%20after%20the%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20cheap%20production%20as%20far%20as%20political%20theatre%20goes%2C%20despite%20the%20considerable%20resources%20invested%20by%20both%20campaigns%20and%20media%20organizations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Reporters%20in%20the%20cavernous%20%26quot%3Bspin%20room%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20Pennsylvania%20Convention%20Center.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e1c8375444ffafa7646ce9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EReporters%20in%20the%20cavernous%20%26quot%3Bspin%20room%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20Pennsylvania%20Convention%20Center.%3Cp%3EBryan%20Dozier%2FVariety%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETuesday%20night's%20debate%2C%20though%20also%20an%20instance%20of%20political%20theatre%2C%20was%20highly%20consequential.%20It%20was%20Harris%20and%20Trump's%20only%20scheduled%20face-off%2C%20though%20the%20vice%20president%20has%20since%20asked%20for%20another.%20But%20the%20spin%20room%20wasn't%20anywhere%20near%20the%20debate%20hall%20at%20the%20National%20Constitution%20Center.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20were%20six%20blocks%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20center%2C%20set%20in%20a%20cavernous%20convention%20center%20hall%20the%20size%20of%20a%20football%20field%2C%20could%20have%20been%20anywhere.%20Six%20giant%20projector%20screens%20displayed%20ABC%20News'%20debate%20stream%2C%20while%20dozens%20of%20rows%20of%20tables%20and%20chairs%20held%20the%20roughly%201%2C000%20reporters%20who%20had%20shown%20up%20for%20the%20ritual.%20Along%20the%20edges%20of%20the%20room%2C%20TV%20anchors%20and%20correspondents%20illuminated%20by%20ring%20lights%20spoke%20into%20their%20cameras.%20Crowds%20of%20reporters%20followed%20surrogates%20like%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr.%20and%20Gov.%20Josh%20Shapiro%20around%20the%20room%20like%20schools%20of%20fish.%20If%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20cover%20the%20debate%20in%20real%20time%2C%20you're%20better%20off%20staying%20at%20home.%20The%20room%20was%20over-air%20conditioned%20and%20prone%20to%20echoes.%20I%20couldn't%20connect%20to%20the%20complimentary%20Wifi.%20The%20%26quot%3Bswag%26quot%3B%20was%20fine%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tote%20bag%2C%20a%20key%20chain%2C%20and%20a%20water%20bottle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Democratic%20Gov.%20Josh%20Shapiro%20of%20Pennsylvania%20finishing%20an%20interview%20with%20CNN%20in%20the%20spin%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e1e2afcfb7f307e5709b77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShapiro%20finishing%20an%20interview%20with%20CNN%20in%20the%20spin%20room.%3Cp%3EChip%20Somodevilla%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20it's%20probably%20the%20only%20scenario%20in%20which%20you%20could%20place%20six%20governors%2C%20nine%20senators%2C%20roughly%20a%20dozen%20House%20members%2C%20and%20a%20host%20of%20other%20political%20celebrities%20before%20hundreds%20of%20reporters%20in%20the%20same%20room%2C%20and%20still%20somehow%20manage%20to%20generate%20almost%20no%20newsworthy%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20largely%20because%2C%20as%20media%20critics%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Farchive.pressthink.org%2F2003%2F11%2F22%2Fspin_alley.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrenuously%20argued%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20decades%2C%20it's%20an%20environment%20where%20candor%20and%20honesty%20are%20in%20short%20supply.%20There's%20a%20message%20to%20deliver%2C%20there's%20a%20victory%20to%20declare%2C%20and%20the%20events%20of%20the%20debate%20itself%20often%20have%20a%20strikingly%20limited%20bearing%20on%20what%20any%20surrogate%20says.%20Before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2F2012-presidential-debates-spin-room_n_1929185%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonset%20of%20Twitter%3C%2Fa%3E%20(now%20known%20as%20X)%2C%20one%20could%20still%20argue%20that%20that%20the%20spin%20room%20played%20an%20important%20role%20within%20our%20conflict-driven%20media%20ecosystem%3A%20In%20such%20an%20environment%2C%20it's%20crucial%20to%20get%20each%20campaign's%20perspective%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20better%20way%20to%20do%20that%20than%20putting%20everyone%20in%20one%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20days%2C%20there's%20a%20zombie-like%20quality%20to%20it.%20You're%20here%20because%20everyone%20else%20is%20here%2C%20and%20this%20is%20how%20we've%20run%20debates%20since%201984.%20We're%20going%20through%20the%20motions.%20If%20you're%20a%20reporter%20looking%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20the%20perspective%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20campaign%2C%20just%20check%20your%20email%20inbox.%20Over%20the%20course%20of%20Tuesday's%20debate%2C%20I%20received%2016%20%26quot%3Bfact%20check%26quot%3B%20emails%20from%20the%20Trump%20campaign%2C%20eight%20such%20emails%20from%20the%20Harris%20campaign%2C%20and%20dozens%20more%20from%20members%20of%20Congress%20and%20downballot%20candidates%20congratulating%20Harris%20and%20Trump%20on%20their%20respective%20%26quot%3Bwins.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20it's%20a%20media%20construct%2C%26quot%3B%20Rep.%20Robert%20Garcia%20told%20me%20ahead%20of%20the%20debate.%20%3Cem%3EDon't%20blame%20me%20for%20participating%20in%20the%20game%20you%20all%20have%20set%20up%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20other%20words.%20This%20was%20the%20media-friendly%20California%20Democrat's%20second%20time%20spinning%20for%20the%20top%20of%20the%20ticket%20this%20year.%20In%20June%2C%20he%20was%20part%20of%20the%20team%20that%20was%20forced%20to%20explain%20away%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-happened-biden-trump-debate-takeaways-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edebate%20performance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20indisputably%20the%20worst%20in%20American%20history.%20Tonight%2C%20his%20job%20would%20undoubtedly%20be%20easier%2C%20but%20I%20wondered%3A%20Was%20he%20prepared%20to%20declare%20Harris%20the%20victor%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20happened%3F%20%26quot%3BWhat%20I'm%20going%20to%20say%20is%20the%20truth%2C%20which%20is%20that%20she's%20going%20to%20perform%20great%20tonight%2C%20because%20she%20always%20does%2C%26quot%3B%20Garcia%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20like%2C%20zero%20doubt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rep.%20Robert%20Garcia%20in%20the%20spin%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e1e32fd17aa3c7b2b1a99f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERep.%20Robert%20Garcia%20in%20the%20spin%20room.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FMatt%20Slocum%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFew%20reporters%20are%20dense%20enough%20to%20outright%20ask%20surrogates%20%26quot%3Bwho%20won%20the%20debate%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bwho's%20going%20to%20win%20the%20debate.%26quot%3B%20And%20most%20of%20us%20understand%20that%20the%20spin%20room%20is%20a%20manifestation%20of%20the%20unholy%20mixture%20of%20news%20and%20entertainment%20that's%20often%20inescapable%20as%20a%20national%20reporter.%20Surrogate%20interviews%20are%20largely%20built%20around%20the%20spinning%20of%20particular%20moments%20or%20themes%20from%20the%20debate.%20Did%20Trump%20come%20across%20as%20too%20frustrated%20and%20angry%3F%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20the%20American%20people%20are%20frustrated%20and%20angry%2C%26quot%3B%20Rep.%20Matt%20Gaetz%20of%20Florida%20explained.%20Did%20Trump%20too%20easily%20take%20Harris'%20bait%3F%20%26quot%3BHe%20did%20some%20things%20that%20were%20a%20little%20unconventional%2C%20but%20I%20think%20that's%20what%20makes%20Donald%20Trump%20such%20a%20compelling%20figure%2C%26quot%3B%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20explained.%20The%20only%20notable%20point%20of%20candor%20to%20emerge%20from%20Tuesday%20night%20was%20from%20Sen.%20Lindsey%20Graham%20of%20South%20Carolina%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebulwark.com%2Fp%2Finside-trump-spin-room-from-hell-presidential-debate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20for%20the%20firing%20of%20Trump's%20debate%20team%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F09%2F11%2Flindsey-graham-trump-debate-00178592%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edescribed%20the%20affair%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmissed%20opportunity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20say%20it%20isn't%20a%20fun%20time%20for%20those%20involved.%20It%20became%20clear%20to%20me%20after%20a%20while%20that%20that's%20why%20we're%20all%20still%20here%2C%20despite%20the%20aforementioned%20vacuousness%20and%20obsolescence%20of%20it%20all.%20If%20you%20care%20what%20Anthony%20Scaramucci%20has%20to%20say%20about%20anything%2C%20as%20the%20Harris%20campaign%20apparently%20thinks%20you%20might%2C%20then%20he's%20on%20hand.%20Remember%20Khizr%20Khan%2C%20the%20Gold%20Star%20father%20from%20the%20Democratic%20convention%20eight%20years%20ago%3F%20Here's%20there%20too.%20And%20where%20else%20can%20one%20use%20the%20urinal%20beside%20a%202024%20GOP%20presidential%20candidate%2C%20as%20I%20unwittingly%20did%20with%20Ramaswamy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20set-up%20also%20laid%20bare%20the%20power%20imbalance%20between%20Republican%20politicians%20and%20right-wing%20media.%20As%20Trump%20spoke%20with%20Fox%20News'%20Sean%20Hannity%2C%20Sens.%20Lindsey%20Graham%20and%20Tim%20Scott%20of%20South%20Carolina%2C%20along%20with%20Ramaswamy%2C%20stood%20patiently%20off%20to%20the%20side%2C%20waiting%20their%20turn%20to%20hit%20the%20airwaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trump%20speaking%20to%20reporters%20in%20the%20spin%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e1e3b1cfb7f307e5709c8e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrump%20speaking%20to%20reporters%20in%20the%20spin%20room.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Dietsch%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20the%20most%20%26quot%3Bnewsworthy%26quot%3B%20thing%20that%20took%20place%20in%20the%20spin%20room%20was%20Trump's%20surprise%20arrival%2C%20which%20triggered%20something%20of%20a%20stampede%20of%20reporters%20toward%20the%20cordoned-off%20bubble%20erected%20around%20him.%20Conventional%20wisdom%20would%20tell%20you%20that%20his%20decision%20to%20show%20up%20is%20a%20sign%20that%20he%20lost%20the%20debate%20%E2%80%94%20why%20bother%20to%20spin%20if%20you%20won%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20the%20former%20president%2C%20larger-than-life%20as%20he%20is%2C%20was%20often%20drowned%20out%20by%20the%20overlapping%20screams%20of%20the%20hundreds%20of%20reporters%20hoping%20to%20get%20his%20attention%2C%20and%20the%20only%20noteworthy%20tidbit%20he%20offered%20was%20a%20noncommittal%20answer%20on%20whether%20he%20would%20agree%20to%20another%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20want%20a%20second%20debate%20because%20they%20lost%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20before%20claiming%20the%20moderators%20were%20working%20against%20him.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20obviously%20three%20on%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-spin-room-presidential-debate-trump-harris-philadelphia-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726084493000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e1ae9a83b8099cf9fd7c0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-spin-room-presidential-debate-trump-harris-philadelphia-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20%26quot%3Bspin%20room%26quot%3B%20might%20be%20the%20only%20time%20you%20can%20put%20multiple%20governors%2C%20senators%2C%20and%20House%20members%20in%20the%20same%20place%20without%20generating%20any%20real%20news.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bmetzger%40insider.com%20(Bryan%20Metzger)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-spin-room-presidential-debate-trump-harris-philadelphia-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%20game%20actors%20fight%20for%20AI%20protections%20and%20compensation%20for%20their%20'digital%20replicas'%20amid%20a%20gaming%20market%20slowdown%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224926%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Girl%20holding%20fist%20up%20in%20picket%20line.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5