aracters%20are%20a%20composite%20of%20different%20motion%20captures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20require%20a%20digital%20replica%20to%20look%2C%20talk%2C%20and%20move%20exactly%20like%20you%20in%20order%20for%20that%20to%20be%20protected.%20If%20you've%20played%20video%20games%20at%20all%2C%20that%20is%20almost%20never%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20Norris%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20negotiations%20take%20place%20amid%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fcc6bd66c-6341-4367-85cc-86d274102378%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslowdown%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20%24200%20billion%20video%20game%20industry.%20Hardware%20sales%20have%20dropped%2C%20and%20game%20developers%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-games-xbox-playstation-spider-man-movie-business-trouble-why-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecutting%20thousands%20of%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Meanwhile%2C%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Fai-is-already-taking-jobs-in-the-video-game-industry%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DGenerative%2520AI%252C%2520by%2520all%2520indications%2Ccompensate%2520for%2520attrition%2520after%2520layoffs.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EActivision%20Blizzard%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20using%20generative%20AI%20tools%20to%20reduce%20costs%20and%20increase%20productivity%20after%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAudrey%20Cooling%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20video%20game%20companies%20involved%20in%20the%20interactive%20media%20negotiations%2C%20said%20that%20the%20studios%20and%20the%20union%20have%20already%20found%20common%20ground%20on%2024%20out%20of%2025%20of%20the%20proposals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20worked%20hard%20to%20deliver%20proposals%20with%E2%80%AFreasonable%E2%80%AFterms%20that%20protect%20the%20rights%20of%20performers%20while%20ensuring%20we%20can%20continue%20to%20use%20the%20most%20advanced%20technology%20to%20create%20great%20entertainment%20experiences%2