0speakers.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHonda%20offers%20a%20premium%2012-speaker%20Bose%20sound%20system%20exclusively%20on%20the%20Sport%20Touring%20trim.%20The%20system%20delivers%20solid%20performance%20and%20comes%20with%20dynamic%20speed%20compensation%2C%20automatically%20adjusting%20volume%20and%20tone%20based%20on%20speed%20and%20road%20noise.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELower%20trim%20level%20CR-Vs%20come%20with%20four%2C%20six%2C%20and%20eight-speaker%20un-branded%20sound%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E15.%20Mesh%20cabin%20accents%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20climate%20controls%20front%20dash%20of%20a%202025%20Honda%20CR-V%20Hybrid%20Sport%20Touring%20SUV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d0de2243b5e59d16b6d783%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20CR-V's%20front%20dash.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20metal%20honeycomb%20mesh%20accent%20spans%20the%20width%20of%20the%20CR-V%20front%20dash.%20It's%20a%20cool%20design%20element%20that%20artfully%20conceals%20the%20CR-V's%20air%20vents.%20The%20metal%20honeycomb%20mesh%20originally%20debuted%20on%20the%20Civic%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E16.%20Handsfree%20liftgate%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20rear%20end%20of%20a%20gray%202025%20Honda%20CR-V%20Hybrid%20Sport%20Touring%20SUV%20parked%20on%20a%20street.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d0d64b43b5e59d16b6d1da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%202025%20Honda%20CR-V%20Hybrid%20Sport%20Touring%20SUV.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAvailable%20only%20on%20the%20Sport%20Touring%20trim%2C%20the%20hands-free%