20has%20been%20overwhelmingly%20positive%20and%20allowed%20her%20to%20connect%20with%20people%20she%20now%20considers%20friends%2C%20they%20have%20read%20a%20few%20negative%20comments%2C%20which%20Grissom%20said%20was%20inevitable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20definitely%20have%20to%20be%20pretty%20confident%20in%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BEverybody's%20got%20opinions.%20You%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20things%2C%20like%2C%20I%20hate%20that%20color.%20I%20hate%20that%20style.%20I%20hate%20the%20thing%20that%20you%20did.%20You%20did%20this%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20couple%20made%20a%20few%20major%20changes%20to%20the%20schoolhouse%20that%20ended%20up%20delaying%20their%20move-in%20plans.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20roof%20needed%20work.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F643695be2588f70018ce6879%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221320%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20installed%20a%20new%20roof.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Stacie%20Grissom%20and%20Sean%20Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20new%20roof%20and%20new%20windows%20are%20the%20two%20most%20expensive%20things%20that%20you%20can%20put%20on%20a%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20Grissom%20said.%20%26quot%3BThose%20were%20the%20two%20daunting%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20couple%20hoped%20to%20be%20finished%20with%20renovation%20by%20November%202023%2C%20complications%20with%20the%20windows%20were%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20their%20move-in%20date%20was%20delayed%20by%20about%20nine%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConstruction%20takes%20a%20lot%20longer%20than%20even%20we%20anticipated%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThings%20were%20slower%2C%20and%20the%20windows%20are%20a%20huge%20part%20of%20it.%20So%20that%20staggered%20other%20things%2C%20like%20when%20we%20were%20able%20to%20get%20the%20floors%20finished%2C%20w