room%20outside%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20like%2C%20'It%20was%20a%20pit%2C'%20and%20I'm%20like%2C%20'Wow%2C%20100%20kids%20and%20a%20pit%20toilet.%20Fascinating.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWilson%20and%20Grissom%20also%20wanted%20to%20honor%20the%20history%20of%20the%20schoolhouse.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Finished%20tiling%20in%20a%20schoolhouse%20that%20was%20turned%20into%20a%20home%20in%20Indiana.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cf89751aa2ac29ee353463%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20wanted%20to%20honor%20the%20history%20of%20their%20home%20by%20incorporating%20nods%20to%20its%20former%20life%20as%20a%20schoolhouse.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Stacie%20Grissom%20and%20Sean%20Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20always%20had%20eclectic%20taste%2C%20collected%20antiques%2C%26quot%3B%20Grissom%2C%20who%20is%20a%20big%20Wes%20Anderson%20fan%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilson%20has%20a%20similar%20style%2C%20so%20they%20shared%20a%20vision%20of%20their%20home%20as%20a%20modern%20space%20with%20homages%20to%20its%20public-school%20origins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20installed%20black%20slate%20tile%20for%20the%20kitchen%20backsplash%2C%20which%20was%20where%20a%20chalkboard%20used%20to%20be.%20In%20another%20part%20of%20the%20house%2C%20they%20used%20tile%20from%20old%20school%20municipal%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20also%20kept%20some%20of%20the%20school's%20original%20pine%20flooring%2C%20which%20thankfully%20remains%20in%20good%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20was%20happy%20to%20preserve%20their%20little%20slice%20of%20Franklin%20history%2C%20not%20just%20for%20themselves%20but%20for%20their%20neighbors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20giant%20building%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20farmland.%20It%20is%20a%20very%20striking%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Grissom%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20means%20a%20lot%20to%20the%20people%20in%20the%20community%20around%20it%2C%20and%20I%20think%20if%20it%20had%20been%20torn%20down%2C%20that%20would've%20been%20really%20sad%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20was%20a%20chance%20that%20the%20schoolhouse%20would%20have%20been%20torn%20down%20if%20the%20couple%20hadn't%20revived%20it.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222047%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Another%20former%20classroom%20in%20the%20schoolhouse.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6437bfd65f081b0019c0f35d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221535%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20schoolhouse%20is%20over%20100%20years%20old.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Stacie%20Grissom%20and%20Sean%20Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20reason%20the%20schoolhouse%20avoided%20getting%20demolished%2C%20a%20fate%20that%20has%20befallen%20other%20older%20buildings%20in%20the%20area%2C%20is%20because%20its%20former%20owners%20were%20passionate%20about%20keeping%20it%20standing%2C%20Grisson%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20tells%20it%2C%20in%201956%2C%20a%20family%20of%20four%20bought%20the%20schoolhouse%20and%20converted%20it%20into%20two%20apartments.%20Grissom%20and%20Wilson%20ended%20up%20buying%20the%20property%20from%20one%20of%20the%20daughters%20of%20the%20former%20owner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20possible%20that%20even%20when%20we%20bought%20it%2C%20it%20would've%20been%20torn%20down.%20So%20we're%20just%20really%2C%20really%20thankful%20to%20the%20family%20that%20came%20before%20us%20that%20they%20kept%20it%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20it%20weren't%20for%20them%2C%20it%20might%20not%20be%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20renovations%20unearthed%20some%20interesting%20vintage%20finds%2C%20like%20this%20clown%20doll.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22896%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20discovered%20a%20creepy%20clown%20doll%20during%20the%20renovation.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6436c7aa2588f70018ce7291%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22673%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20discovered%20a%20clown%20doll%20during%20the%20renovation.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Stacie%20Grissom%20and%20Sean%20Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20found%20what%20Grissom%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bweird%20clown%20doll%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20renovation%2C%20but%20have%20no%20idea%20of%20its%20origins.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20doll%20and%20a%20few%20crickets%20in%20the%20basement%2C%20they%20haven't%20made%20many%20other%20discoveries.%20However%2C%20they%20have%C2%A0stumbled%20across%20some%20wild%20tales%20from%20people%20in%20the%20community%20and%20local%20museums.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20crazy%20stories%2C%26quot%3B%20Grissom%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20tales%20that%20stuck%20out%20came%20from%20a%20former%20owner%20who%20also%20attended%20the%20school%20as%20a%20child.%20She%20told%20Grissom%20and%20Wilson%20that%20she%20remembers%20two%20boys%20getting%20in%20trouble%20with%20the%20principal%20for%20setting%20up%20a%20live%20wire%20attached%20to%20an%20engine%20in%20the%20basement%20to%20the%20principal's%20door%20handle%20as%20a%20prank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20just%20like%2C%20'That%20would%20never%20happen%20today%2C'%26quot%3B%20Grissom%20said%20with%20a%20laugh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThey%20don't%20regret%20buying%20the%20schoolhouse%2C%20but%20Grissom%20said%20renovating%20it%20was%20more%20of%20a%20challenge%20than%20they%20anticipated.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222131%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stacie%20Grissom%20wearing%20overalls%20and%20smiling%20as%20she%20stands%20in%20her%20renovated%20schoolhouse.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e1ade15444ffafa7645b44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221598%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGrissom%20is%20happy%20the%20family%20will%20finally%20be%20able%20to%20move%20into%20the%20schoolhouse%20in%202024.%3Cp%3ERoy%20Ritchie%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20joy%20as%20the%20renovation%20and%20documenting%20it%20online%20has%20brought%20Grissom%20and%20Wilson%2C%20she%20said%20there%20were%20also%20really%20difficult%20moments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20renovations%20like%20this%2C%20it%20just%20kind%20of%20beats%20you%20down%20over%20time%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20allow%20yourself%20to%20get%20excited%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20definitely%20still%20very%20glad%20we%20did%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20doesn't%20have%20any%20regrets%2C%20she%20said%20she%20and%20Wilson%20probably%20wouldn't%20consider%20taking%20on%20a%20similar%20project%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWould%20we%20do%20it%20again%3F%20I%20don't%20know%2C%20I've%20got%20to%20recover%20from%20the%20PTSD%20of%20it%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20Grissom%20joked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20key%20lesson%20the%20couple%20learned%20is%20to%20trust%20their%20guts%20when%20hiring%20people%20to%20help%20with%20the%20renovation.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Builders%20constructing%20a%20garage%20at%20a%20schoolhouse%20in%20Indiana.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cf900a397a168972023e6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFinding%20the%20right%20team%20to%20renovate%20a%20home%20is%20essential%2C%20Grissom%20said.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Stacie%20Grissom%20and%20Sean%20Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20make%20sure%20you're%20working%20with%20the%20right%20people%20during%20a%20sensitive%20renovation%2C%20Grissom%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20and%20Wilson%20had%20the%20most%20trouble%20when%20they%20made%20a%20few%20hiring%20mistakes.%20A%20piece%20of%20advice%20they'd%20give%20others%20renovating%20old%20houses%20is%20to%20check%20references%20carefully.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20already%20know%20someone%20you're%20hiring%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20know%20them%20personally%2C%20or%20you%20don't%20know%20someone%20who%20knows%20them%20personally%2C%20call%20references%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20something%20feels%20off%2C%20she%20also%20recommends%20trusting%20your%20gut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20start%20to%20develop%20an%20instinct%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20personal%20to%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENow%20that%20Grissom%20and%20Wilson%20have%20finally%20moved%20in%2C%20they're%20excited%20to%20embark%20on%20smaller%20projects%2C%20like%20a%20cocktail%20cellar.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20brick-lined%20boiler%20room%20in%20an%20old%20schoolhouse%20in%20Indiana%20that%20is%20being%20converted%20into%20a%20cocktail%20cellar.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cf8f79397a168972023d5a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20plan%20to%20turn%20an%20old%20boiler%20room%20into%20a%20swanky%20cocktail%20cellar.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Stacie%20Grissom%20and%20Sean%20Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20the%20schoolhouse%20is%20livable%2C%20Grissom%20said%20she%20and%20Wilson%20can%20start%20making%20smaller%20upgrades%20that%20will%20be%20less%20laborious%2C%20less%20time-consuming%2C%20and%20more%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20exciting%20projects%20is%20their%20plan%20to%20convert%20the%20school's%20old%20boiler%20room%20that%20dates%20to%20the%201940s%20into%20an%20at-home%20cocktail%20cellar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20we're%20like%2C%20'OK%2C