e-fans-react-watch%2Farticleshow%2F113269810.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chief%20Minister%20Nayab%20Saini%20Vs%20Sitting%20MLA%3A%20Who%20Has%20The%20Edge%20In%20Ladwa%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECarved%20out%20as%20a%20separate%20constituency%20only%20in%202009%2C%20the%20Ladwa%20Assembly%20seat%20in%20Haryana%20has%20all%20eyes%20on%20it%20ahead%20of%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20state%20because%20the%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20Chief%20Minister%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20from%20there%20and%20he%20is%20seen%20to%20be%20facing%20a%20tough%20contest%20from%20sitting%20MLA%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Mewa%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20BJP%20eyeing%20a%20third%20consecutive%20victory%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20state%20and%20declaring%20Mr%20Saini%2C%20who%20took%20over%20as%20chief%20minister%20from%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20in%20March%2C%20as%20its%20chief%20ministerial%20face%2C%20NDTV%20visited%20the%20Ladwa%20constituency%20and%20spoke%20to%20people%20there%2C%20as%20well%20as%20both%20candidates%2C%20to%20get%20a%20feel%20of%20which%20party%20has%20the%20edge%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20voter%20in%20the%20constituency%2C%20Sanjiv%20Sahni%2C%20said%20the%20main%20issues%20are%20inflation%2C%20unemployment%20and%20a%20bypass%20that%20was%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20has%20had%20a%20government%20here%20for%2010%20years.%20Before%20coming%20to%20power%2C%20they%20made%20many%20promises%2C%20including%20that%20a%20bypass%20would%20be%20built%20and%202%20crore%20people%20would%20get%20employment.%20But%20it%20didn't%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20voter%20said%20Mr%20Saini%20was%20an%20MP%20from%20the%20Kurukshetra%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20of%20which%20the%20Ladwa%20segment%20is%20a%20part%2C%20but%20his%20presence%20had%20not%20been%20felt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisagreeing%20with%20the%20others%2C%20a%20