C000%20votes%20in%20June%2C%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20the%20Ladwa%20constituency%20because%20it%20has%20a%20high%20population%20of%20voters%20from%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Communities%20(OBCs)%2C%20particularly%20the%20Saini%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20the%20BJP's%20Naveen%20Jindal%20won%20from%20the%20Kurukshetra%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20of%20which%20the%20Ladwa%20segment%20is%20a%20part%2C%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20over%2029%2C000%20votes%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20have%20played%20a%20part%20in%20the%20decision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOBC's%20make%20up%2040.09%25%20of%20the%20population%20in%20the%20constituency%20with%20the%20Saini%20community%20alone%20accounting%20for%2018.92%25.%20Among%20non-OBC%20communities%2C%20Jats%20are%20a%20sizeable%20part%20of%20the%20population%2C%20making%20up%2015.84%25.%20The%20constituency%20has%201.95%20lakh%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20constituency%20was%20carved%20out%20from%20the%20Thanesar%20Assembly%20segment%20in%202009%20and%20no%20party%20has%20won%20it%20twice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%20will%20vote%20on%20October%205%20and%20counting%20will%20be%20held%20on%20October%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726078620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fgosa5re_nayab_625x300_07_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-assembly-elections-chief-minister-nayab-saini-vs-sitting-mla-who-has-the-edge-in-ladwa-6544039%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Carved%20out%20as%20a%20separate%20constituency%20only%20in%202009%2C%20the%20Ladwa%20Assembly%20seat%20in%20Haryana%20has%20all%20eyes%20on%20it%20ahead%20of%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20state%20because%20the%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20Chief%20Minister%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20from%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ajit%20Doval%20In%20Moscow%20With%20Ukraine%20Peace%20Plan%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20Says%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia%20Ready%20To...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERussia%20and%20Ukraine%20will%20have%20to%20resolve%20their%20conflict%20by%20negotiating%20off%20the%20battlefield%20and%20India%20is%20willing%20to%20advise%20them%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishakar's%20remarks%20came%20at%20a%20time%20when%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20Ajit%20Doval%20is%20in%20Moscow%20for%20a%20crucial%20meeting%20of%20NSAs.%20Sources%20have%20said%20that%20Mr%20Doval%20is%20carrying%20a%20peace%20plan%20proposed%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20which%20he%20will%20share%20with%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Flmin2r3_ajit-doval-moscow_625x300_11_September_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20or%20not%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20accept%20India's%20proposal%20is%20not%20known%20yet%2C%20but%20India%20has%20offered%20to%20help%20end%20the%20conflict.%20During%20his%20visit%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20PM%20Modi%20told%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20that%20India%20is%20ever%20ready%20to%20play%20an%20%26quot%3Bactive%20role%26quot%3B%20in%20every%20effort%20to%20restore%20peace%20and%20he%20would%20like%20to%20contribute%20personally%20in%20ending%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20is%20perhaps%20one%20of%20the%20very%20few%20leaders%20who%20shares%20friendly%20ties%20with%20both%20Mr%20Putin%20and%20Mr%20Zelensky%20and%20was%20warmly%20welcomed%20by%20both%20leaders%20during%20his%20recent%20visits%20to%20both%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D