ff%20the%20balcony%20of%20his%20sixth-floor%20residence%20in%20Bandra's%20Ayesha%20Manor%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20tired%26quot%3B.%20The%20police%20have%20said%20Mehta%20died%20by%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehta's%20wife%20and%20Malaika%20and%20Amrita%20Arora's%20mother%2C%20Joyce%20Polycarp%2C%20has%20told%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20that%20she%20was%20in%20the%20house%20when%20the%20incident%20took%20place.%20Around%209%20am%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20she%20noticed%20her%20husband's%20slippers%20in%20the%20living%20room%20and%20began%20looking%20for%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20agency%20IANS%2C%20when%20she%20didn't%20find%20him%20in%20the%20balcony%2C%20she%20leaned%20over%20the%20railing%20and%20noticed%20that%20there%20was%20a%20commotion%20and%20a%20security%20guard%20in%20the%20building%20was%20shouting%20for%20help.%20This%2C%20she%20told%20the%20cops%2C%20was%20when%20she%20realised%20something%20was%20terribly%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IANS%20report%20said%20Anil%20had%20called%20both%20his%20daughters%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20tired%26quot%3B%2C%20before%20allegedly%20jumping%20off%20the%20balcony.%20Malaika%20Arora%20was%20headed%20to%20an%20event%20in%20Pune%20at%20the%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20post-mortem%20is%20being%20conducted%20at%20Bhabha%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalaika%20Arora%20was%20born%20in%20Thane%20near%20Mumbai.%20Her%20parents%20got%20divorced%20when%20she%20was%2011%20and%20she%20moved%20to%20Chembur%20with%20her%20mother%2C%20Joyce%2C%20and%20sister%2C%20Amrita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoyce%20Polycarp%20is%20a%20Malayali%20Christian%20while%20Anil%20Mehta%20was%20from%20the%20Punjabi%20community%20and%20worked%20in%20the%20Indian%20Merchant%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalaika's%20former%20husband%20Arbaaz%20Khan%20and%20her%20rumoured%20ex-boyfriend%20Arjun%20Kapoor%20also%20reportedly%20went%20to%20the%20apartment%20after%20getting%20news%20of%20Mehta's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20interview%20with%20a%20fashion%20magazine%2C%20Malaika%20had%20spoken%20about%20her%20parents'%20divorce%20and%20said%20that%20even%20though%20her%20childhood%20was%20%26quot%3Bwonderful%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Btumultous%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bnot%20easy%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20IANS%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20parents'%20separation%20allowed%20me%20to%20observe%20my%20mother%20through%20a%20new%20lens%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B919999666555%5C%22%3E9999666555%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%5C%22%3Ehelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ETISS%20iCall%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B912225521111%5C%22%3E022-25521111%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Monday-Saturday%3A%208%20am%20to%2010%20pm)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E(If%20you%20need%20support%20or%20know%20someone%20who%20does%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20your%20nearest%20mental%20health%20specialist.)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726076400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F95ih6qp_malaika-arora-_625x300_11_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftired-what-malaika-aroras-father-told-her-before-jumping-off-building-6543669%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Releasing%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20death%20of%20her%20father%2C%20Anil%20Kuldip%20Mehta%2C%20who%20allegedly%20jumped%20from%20his%20apartment%20building%20in%20Mumbai's%20Bandra%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20actor%20Malaika%20Arora%20has%20said%20that%20the%20family%20is%20in%20deep%20s