0Narendra%20Modi%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%20(AB%20PM-JAY)%20will%20benefit%204.5%20crore%20families%20with%20six%20crore%20senior%20citizens.%20The%20free%20cover%20is%20worth%20Rs%205%20lakh%20and%20will%20be%20on%20a%20family%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20this%20approval%2C%20all%20senior%20citizens%20of%20the%20age%2070%20years%20and%20above%20irrespective%20of%20their%20socio-%20economic%20status%20would%20be%20eligible%20to%20avail%20the%20benefits%20of%20AB%20PM-JAY.%20The%20eligible%20senior%20citizens%20would%20be%20issued%20a%20new%20distinct%20card%20under%20AB%20PM-JAY%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20citizens%20of%20the%20age%2070%20years%20and%20above%20belonging%20to%20families%20already%20covered%20under%20AB%20PM-JAY%20will%20get%20an%20additional%20top-up%20cover%20up%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%20per%20year%20for%20themselves%20(which%20they%20do%20not%20have%20to%20share%20with%20other%20members%20of%20the%20family%20who%20are%20below%20the%20age%20of%2070%20years)%2C%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20citizens%20above%2070%20who%20are%20already%20getting%20benefits%20of%20other%20public%20health%20insurance%20schemes%20such%20as%20Central%20Government%20Health%20Scheme%20(CGHS)%2C%20Ex-Servicemen%20Contributory%20Health%20Scheme%20(ECHS)%2C%20and%20Ayushman%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Force%20(CAPF)%20may%20either%20choose%20their%20existing%20scheme%20or%20opt%20for%20AB%20PMJAY.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EJoined%20Ganesh%20Puja%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20CJI%2C%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20Ji.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMay%20Bhagwan%20Shri%20Ganesh%20bless%20us%20all%20with%20happiness%2C%20prosperity%20and%20wonderful%20health.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FdfWlR7elky%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FdfWlR7elky%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1833908774051926135%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20clarified%20that%20senior%20citizens%20of%2070%20years%20and%20above%20who%20are%20under%20private%20health%20insurance%20policies%20or%20Employees'%20State%20Insurance%20Scheme%20will%20be%20eligible%20to%20avail%20benefits%20under%20AB%20PM-JAY.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AB%20PM-JAY%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20publicly%20funded%20health%20assurance%20scheme%20which%20provides%20health%20cover%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20per%20family%20per%20year%20for%20secondary%20and%20tertiary%20care%20hospitalisation%20to%2055%20crore%20people%2C%20corresponding%20to%2012.34%20crore%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20members%20of%20eligible%20families%20irrespective%20of%20age%20are%20covered%20under%20the%20scheme.%20The%20scheme%20has%20covered%207.37%20crore%20hospital%20admissions%20including%2049%20per%20cent%20women%20beneficiaries.%20The%20public%20has%20benefited%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20over%20Rs%201%20lakh%20crore%20under%20the%20scheme%2C%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expansion%20of%20cover%20to%20senior%20citizens%20of%2070%20and%20above%20was%20announced%20by%20PM%20Modi%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20said%20the%20AB%20PM-JAY%20scheme%20has%20seen%20continuous%20expansion%20of%20the%20beneficiary%20base.%20Initially%2C%2010.74%20crore%20poor%20and%20vulnerable%20families%20comprising%20the%20bottom%2040%20per%20cent%20of%20India's%20population%20were%20covered%20under%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20the%20government%20in%20January%202022%20revised%20the%20beneficiary%20base%20under%20AB%20PM-JAY%20from%2010.74%20crore%20to%2012%20crore%20families%20considering%20India's%20decadal%20population%20growth%20of%2011.7%20per%20cent%20over%202011%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20was%20further%20expanded%20to%20cover%2037%20lakh%20ASHAs%2FAWWs%2FAWHs%20working%20across%20the%20country%20and%20their%20families%20for%20free%20healthcare%20benefits.%20Taking%20the%20mission%20ahead%2C%20AB%20PM-JAY%20would%20now%20provide%20free%20healthcare%20coverage%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20to%20%C2%A0all%20citizens%20of%20the%20age-group%20of%2070%20years%20and%20above%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726075200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-01%2Fqrkq57t_coronavirus-india-generic-hospital-generic-covid-hospital-reuters-650_625x300_10_January_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feveryone-whos-over-70-years-old-to-be-covered-under-the-health-insurance-scheme-ayushman-bharat-centre-6542584%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20centre%20has%20decided%20to%20cover%20everyone%20who%20is%20over%2070%20years%20old%20under%20the%20health%20insurance%20scheme%20Ayushman%20Bharat.%20The%20scheme%20will%20now%20cover%20everyone%20aged%2070%20or%20above%20despite%20their%20economical%20background.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feveryone-whos-over-70-years-old-to-be-covered-under-the-health-insurance-scheme-ayushman-bharat-centre-6542584%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20the%20world%20thought%20of%20US%20debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726075163000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0351%2Flive%2Fda47a040-704b-11ef-8c1a-df523ba43a9a.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc9wj9qejrpwo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20the%20Harris-Trump%20debate%20was%20seen%20from%20Putin's%20Kremlin%2C%20Ukraine's%20frontlines%20and%20Taliban-run%20Afghanistan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A327%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc9wj9qejrpwo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc9wj9qejrpwo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc9wj9qejrpwo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20economy%20has%20finally%20taken%20off%2C%20says%20veteran%20banker%20Deepak%20Parekh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726075153000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-02%2F28%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1709058779-1542.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findian-economy-has-finally-taken-off-says-veteran-banker-deepak-parekh-124091101495_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20manufacturing%2C%20infra%20cos%20should%20invest%20more%2C%20says%20veteran%20banker%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findian-economy-has-finally-taken-off-says-veteran-banker-deepak-parekh-124091101495_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findian-economy-has-finally-taken-off-says-veteran-banker-deepak-parekh-124091101495_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findian-economy-has-finally-taken-off-says-veteran-banker-deepak-parekh-124091101495_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Protesters%20Seek%20Demolition%20Of%20%26quot%3BIllegal%26quot%3B%20Portion%20Of%20Mosque%2C%20Clash%20With%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EProtesters%20demanding%20the%20demolition%20of%20an%20illegal%20portion%20of%20a%20mosque%20in%20Shimla's%20Sanjauli%20area%20clashed%20with%20security%20personnel%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20breaking%20barricades%20and%20throwing%20stones%20as%20police%20used%20water%20cannons%20and%20lathi-charged%20them.%20Ten%20people%20including%20policemen%20and%20women%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic%20Works%20Minister%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20said%20the%20government%20was%20concerned%20over%20escalation%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20was%20keeping%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20all%20the%20developments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20central%20leadership%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20and%20myself%20have%20talked%20to%20party%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20party%20in-charge%20Rajiv%20Shukla%20and%20they%20are%20also%20concerned%20that%20there%20was%20no%20deterioration%20in%20law%20and%20order%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20protesters%20gathered%20at%20the%20Sabzi%20Mandi%20Dhalli%20and%20marched%20towards%20Sanjauli%20market%2C%20defying%20prohibitory%20orders%20and%20ignoring%20warnings%20by%20the%20administration.%20They%20broke%20barricades%20erected%20near%20the%20Dhalli%20tunnel%20while%20another%20crowd%20gathered%20at%20Sanjauli%20Chowk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20protesters%20gathered%20on%20the%20call%20of%20some%20Hindu%20groups%20entered%20Sanjauli%20and%20broke%20a%20second%20barricade%20near%20the%20mosque%2C%20police%20baton%20charged%20and%20used%20water%20cannons%20to%20disperse%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20detained%20some%20protesters%20as%20well%2C%20including%20Hindu%20Jagran%20Manch%20secretary%20Kamal%20Gautam%2C%20and%20erected%20the%20barricade%20near%20the%20mosque%20again%2C%20but%20the%20protesters%20refused%20to%20leave%20and%20continued%20raising%20slogans%20against%20the%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outbreak%20of%20the%20clash%20left%20students%20in%20Sanjauli%2C%20Dhalli%20and%20adjoining%20areas%20stranded%20in%20schools.%20Residents%20vented%20their%20anger%20at%20the%20administration%20for%20not%20ordering%20the%20schools%20to%20remain%20closed%20for%20the%20day%20despite%20being%20aware%20of%20the%20demonstration.%20They%20said%20several%20school%20managements%20are%20awaiting%20directions%20from%20the%20district%20administration%20to%20send%20the%20children%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20protest%20against%20the%20baton%20charge%2C%20the%20Shimla%20Beopar%20Mandal%20has%20called%20a%20bandh%20on%20Thursday.%20Mandal%20president%20Sanjeev%20Thakur%20said%20the%20bandh%20would%20be%20from%2010%20am%20to%201%20pm%2C%20and%20protests%20would%20be%20held%20at%20various%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikramaditya%20Singh%20said%20Hindus%20have%20the%20right%20to%20protest%20peacefully%2C%20but%20no%20one%20would%20be%20allowed%20to%20take%20the%20law%20in%20their%20hands.%20He%20told%20reporters%20that%20as%20far%20as%20the%20issue%20of%20unauthorised%20construction%20in%20the%20mosque%20is%20concerned%2C%20the%20case%20is%20pending%20in%20the%20court%20of%20the%20Shimla%20Municipal%20Corporation%20Commissioner%20and%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20as%20per%20the%20law%20once%20the%20decision%20comes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20construction%20is%20unauthorised%2C%20the%20structure%20would%20be%20demolished%20according%20to%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20case%20is%20pending%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years%20and%20there%20were%20mayors%20of%20CPI(M)%20and%20BJP%20also%20in%20the%20past%2C%20so%20no%20politics%20should%20be%20done%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20lives%20peacefully%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20which%20is%20also%20known%20as%20'dev%20bhoomi'%20and%20I%20appeal%20to%20the%20people%20not%20to%20take%20law%20in%20their%20hands%2C%26quot%3B%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20six%20police%20personnel%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20scuffle%20and%20stone-throwing%2C%20while%20four%20protesters%20were%20injured%2C%20DGP%20Atul%20Verma%20who%20was%20at%20the%20spot%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20tried%20to%20pacify%20the%20situation%20through%20dialogue%20but%20there%20is%20no%20leader%20and%20the%20mob%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20listen%2C%26quot%3B%20SP%20Shimla%20Sanjeev%20Kumar%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20protesters%20Kalpi%20Sharma%20said%2015%20people%20including%20women%20were%20injured.%20Vijay%20Sharma%2C%20who%20led%20the%20protest%2C%20said%20the%20police%20baton%20charged%20them%20and%20that%20led%20to%20the%20volatile%20atmosphere%20in%20the%20area.%20Sunita%2C%20who%20was%20among%20the%20protesters%2C%20said%20the%20police%20baton%20charged%20children%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20neither%20from%20the%20Congress%20nor%20the%20BJP.%20We%20are%20Hindus%20and%20want%20these%20street%20vendors%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJanvi%2C%20a%20student%20of%20Class%206%20of%20SPM%20Public%20School%20in%20Sanjauli%2C%20said%20the%20students%20were%20scared%20as%20they%20were%20stuck%20in%20school%20due%20to%20the%20protest.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20allowed%20to%20leave%20when%20our%20parents%20came%20to%20collect%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20protesters%20alleged%20the%20government%20first%20denied%20them%20permission%20to%20hold%20a%20peaceful%20demonstration%20and%20now%2C%20was%20arresting%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20demand%20that%20the%20structure%20be%20sealed%20till%20the%20hearing%20is%20concluded%2C%20all%20outsiders%20coming%20to%20the%20state%20be%20registered%20and%20a%20vendor's%20policy%20formulated%20on%20a%20population%20basis%20with%2095%20per%20cent%20licence%20to%20Hindus%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinister%20Singh%20said%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20state%20in%20the%20country%20to%20act%20against%20conversion%20during%20Congress%20rule%20when%20Virbhadra%20Singh%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20I%20am%20proud%20to%20be%20a%20Hindu%20but%20the%20government%20works%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20law%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20sensitive%20towards%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20stand%20with%20them%20but%20minorities%20are%20also%20a%20part%20of%20the%20state%20and%20we%20have%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20stop%20anybody%20from%20coming%20to%20the%20state%20to%20earn%20livelihood%20but%20we%20have%20to%20strengthen%20our%20internal%20security%20and%20verification%20of%20outsiders%20coming%20to%20the%20state%20would%20be%20done%20by%20the%20police%20as%20well%20as%20the%20municipal%20corporation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20maintained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20women%20also%20joined%20the%20protest%20and%20recited%20Hanuman%20Chalisa%20at%20Dhalli%20before%20breaking%20the%20barricades.%20The%20Shimla%20district%20administration%20had%20issued%20prohibitory%20orders%20under%20Section%20163%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%2C%20barring%20the%20gathering%20of%20five%20or%20more%20people%20and%20carrying%20of%20lethal%20weapons%20and%20arms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Jai%20Ram%20Thakur%20appealed%20to%20the%20protesters%20not%20to%20defy%20the%20prohibitory%20orders.%20%26quot%3BThe%20case%20of%20the%20unauthorised%20mosque%20is%20very%20sensitive%20and%20should%20not%20be%20dealt%20with%20routinely%20and%20the%20matter%20should%20be%20expedited%20as%20tension%20can%20spill%20over%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20also%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20said%20the%20issue%20should%20not%20be%20given%20a%20political%20colour.%20%26quot%3BMaintaining%20law%20and%20order%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20government.%20People%20have%20the%20right%20to%20protest%20peacefully%20but%20there%20should%20be%20no%20damage%20to%20anyone%20from%20any%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindu%20organisations%20demanding%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20disputed%20structure%20in%20the%20mosque%20and%20the%20registration%20of%20outsiders%20coming%20to%20the%20state%20had%20given%20the%20call%20for%20the%20Sanjauli%20bandh%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Last%20Thursday%2C%20Hindu%20groups%20staged%20massive%20protests%20at%20the%20Chaura%20Maidan%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20and%20Sanjauli%20to%20press%20for%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726075080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Ftnn1k8d8_shimla_625x300_11_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshimla-mosque-dispute-protesters-break-barricades-clash-with-police-10-injured-6542897%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Protesters%20demanding%20the%20demolition%20of%20an%20illegal%20portion%20of%20a%20mosque%20in%20Shimla's%20Sanjauli%20area%20clashed%20with%20security%20personnel%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshimla-mosque-dispute-protesters-break-barricades-clash-with-police-10-injured-6542897%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Finance%20ministry%20allows%20GST%20deductions%20to%20dealers%20on%20demo%20vehicles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726074929000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-08%2F22%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1724303809-2243.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Ffinance-ministry-allows-gst-deductions-to-dealers-on-demo-vehicles-124091101509_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Another%20circular%20on%20supply%20of%20data%20hosting%20services%20was%20issued%20where%20such%20services%20are%20provided%20by%20companies%20in%20India%20to%20cloud%20computing%20service%20providers%20loc