sity%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20kept%20him%20confined%20to%20a%20room%20for%20the%20entire%20night%2C%20thrashed%20him%20and%20whipped%20him%20with%20a%20belt.%20His%20crime%3F%20The%20students%20wanted%20him%20to%20drink%20alcohol%20and%20he%20refused.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assault%20on%20the%20student%20was%20caught%20on%20camera%20and%20five%20of%20his%20college%20mates%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20younger%20than%20him%2C%20have%20been%20arrested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20filed%20in%20the%20case%2C%2022-year-old%20Rajat%20Kumar%2C%20a%20first-year%20MBA%20student%20at%20Bahra%20University%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh's%20Solan%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20the%20university%20hostel%2C%20was%20asked%20by%20two%20of%20his%20fellow%20students%20to%20accompany%20them%20to%20another%20room%20on%20Saturday.%20When%20Kumar%20refused%2C%20they%20dragged%20him%20to%20the%20room%2C%20where%20a%20few%20other%20students%20were%20present.%20The%20students%20asked%20Kumar%20to%20consume%20alcohol%20and%20beat%20him%20up%20-%20raining%20kicks%20and%20punches%20and%20whipping%20him%20with%20a%20belt%20-%20when%20he%20refused.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%2C%20which%20appears%20to%20be%20shot%20by%20a%20student%20on%20his%20cellphone%2C%20shows%20Kumar%20sitting%20on%20a%20chair%2C%20facing%20a%20few%20other%20students.%20A%20conversation%20takes%20place%20and%20when%20the%20word%20complaint%20is%20mentioned%2C%20one%20of%20the%20students%20stands%20up%20menacingly%2C%20moves%20close%20to%20Kumar%20and%20slaps%20him.%20He%20is%20made%20to%20sit%20down%20by%20another%20student%2C%20who%20has%20his%20arm%20around%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apparent%20saviour%20turns%20into%20an%20assaulter%20himself%20soon%20after%2C%20however%2C%20launching%20a%20volley%20of%20abuses%20at%20Kumar%20and%20slapping%20him.%20The%20second%20student%20slaps%20Kumar%20again%20and%20the%20first%20gets%20up%2C%20picks%20up%20a%20belt%20and%20starts%20whipping%20him.%20The%20video%20shows%20Kumar%20also%20being%20punched%20by%20the%20students%20as%20the%20other%20people%20in%20the%20room%20remain%20mute%20spectators.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20conversation%20and%20the%20assault%20continues%2C%20one%20of%20the%20students%20approaches%20Kumar%20with%20a%20bottle%20of%20liquor%20and%20a%20glass%20and%20offers%20him%20a%20peg%2C%20directing%20him%20to%20drink%20it%20and%20then%20become%20a%20%3Cem%3E'murga'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sit%20in%20a%20semi-squatting%20posture%20as%20a%20punishment).%20Kumar%20refuses%20to%20have%20the%20drink%20and%20says%20he%20made%20a%20mistake%2C%20but%20one%20of%20the%20assaulters%20asks%20him%20to%20have%20a%20beer%20if%20he%20does%20not%20want%20hard%20liquor.%20The%20student%20instructs%20one%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20room%20to%20get%20the%20beer%20quickly%20and%20warns%20him%20that%20he%20would%20be%20beaten%20up%20if%20he%20did%20not%20comply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArrests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20initiated%20an%20inquiry%20against%20Kumar's%20assaulters%20and%20the%20anti-ragging%20committee%20asked%20them%20to%20appear%20before%20it%2C%20but%20the%20students%20refused.%20Solan%20Suprintendent%20of%20Police%20Gaurav%20Singh%20said%20Kumar%20filed%20a%20complaint%20at%20the%20Kandaghat%20police%20station%2C%20which%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20the%20students%20under%20sections%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20and%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Educational%20Institutions%20(Prohibition%20of%20Ragging)%20Act%2C%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Ftj6btpb8_himachal-ragging_625x300_11_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20students%20-%20Chirag%20Rana%2C%20Divyansh%20and%20