%20I%20am%20against%20reservation.%20But%20let%20me%20make%20it%20clear%20%E2%80%93%20I%20am%20not%20against%20reservation.%20We%20will%20take%20reservation%20beyond%20the%20limit%20of%2050%20per%20cent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20during%20an%20interview%20at%20the%20National%20Press%20Club%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comment%20that%20sparked%20controversy%20was%20made%20during%20an%20interaction%20with%20the%20students%20and%20the%20faculty%20of%20Georgetown%20University%20in%20Washington%20DC%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20will%20%26quot%3Bthink%20of%20ending%20reservation%20when%20India%20is%20a%20fair%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20added%2C%20India%20is%20not%20a%20fair%20place%20at%20the%20moment%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BThe%20elephant%20in%20the%20room%20is%20that%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20India%20--%20OBCs%2C%20Dalits%20and%20Adivasis%20don't%20play%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCaste%20census%20is%20a%20simple%20exercise%20to%20know%20how%20the%20lower%20castes%2C%20backward%20castes%20and%20Dalits%20are%20integrated%20into%20the%20system...Out%20of%20the%20top%20200%20businesses%20in%20India%2C%20there%20is%20almost%20no%20ownership%20of%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20population%20of%20India.%20In%20the%20highest%20courts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20there%20is%20almost%20no%20participation%20of%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20India.%20In%20media%2C%20there%20is%20zero%20participation%20of%20lower%20castes%2C%20OBCs%2C%20Dalits%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20explaining%20the%20idea%20behind%20the%20caste%20census%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20understand%20what%20their%20social%20and%20financial%20position%20looks%20like...We%20also%20want%20to%20look%20at%20the%20Indian%20institutions%20to%20have%20a%20sense%20of%20India's%20participation%20in%20these%20institutions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20comments%20on%