lds%20the%20constitutional%20position%20of%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20This%20role%20entails%20greater%20responsibilities%2C%20and%20his%20statements%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20taken%20more%20seriously.%20This%20visit%20to%20the%20U.S.%20marks%20his%20first%20in%20this%20new%20role%20after%20the%20recently%20concluded%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAudiences%20in%20the%20U.S.%20who%20may%20not%20be%20familiar%20with%20the%20nuances%20of%20Indian%20politics%20or%20have%20personal%20experiences%20of%20the%20situation%20might%20take%20his%20words%20at%20face%20value%2C%20potentially%20forming%20a%20negative%20opinion%20about%20India%2C%20a%20country%20that%20is%20rapidly%20making%20its%20presence%20felt%20as%20an%20emerging%20economic%20power%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20one%20thing%20for%20an%20opposition%20leader%20to%20criticize%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20government%20domestically%2C%20but%20Gandhi%20often%20ends%20up%20disparaging%20his%20own%20country%2C%20its%20people%2C%20and%20its%20institutions%20on%20foreign%20soil.%20He%20seems%20to%20aim%20at%20showcasing%20his%20deep%20understanding%20of%20not%20just%20Indian%20polity%2C%20economy%2C%20and%20society%20but%20also%20Hinduism%2C%20spirituality%2C%20and%20the%20global%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20doing%20so%2C%20he%20begins%20to%20praise%20China's%20advancements%20while%20downplaying%20India's%20achievements%2C%20as%20he%20did%20upon%20arriving%20in%20the%20U.S.%20He%20seems%20indifferent%20to%20whether%20he%20wants%20India%20to%20adopt%20a%20Chinese-style%20polity%20or%20if%20his%20portrayal%20of%20China's%20development%20and%20employment%20practices%20is%20factually%20accurate%20or%20merely%20his%20perception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20supporters%20become%20active%2C%20pointing%20out%20to%20anyone%20who%20will%20listen%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20once%20again%20made%20controversial%20statements%20abroad%2C%20almost%20as%20if%20he%20is%20a%20habitual%20offender.%20The%20argument%20is%20that%20when%20he%20makes%20similar%20comments%20to%20a%20domestic%20audience%2C%20people%20can%20form%20their%20own%20judgments%20based%20on%20their%20experiences%2C%20whether%20right%20or%20wrong.%20However%2C%20the%20same%20does%20not%20apply%20when%20he%20makes%20such%20statements%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20visit%20to%20America%2C%20Gandhi%20questioned%20a%20Sikh%20in%20the%20audience%20about%20his%20name%20and%20then%20commented%20on%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20Sikhs%20in%20India%20regarding%20their%20religious%20symbols%20and%20practices.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BFirst%20of%20all%2C%20you%20have%20to%20understand%20what%20the%20fight%20is%20about.%20The%20fight%20is%20not%20about%20politics.%20It%20is%20superficial.%20What%20is%20your%20name%3F%20The%20fight%20is%20about%20whether%20he%20as%20a%20Sikh%20is%20going%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20wear%20his%20turban%20in%20India.%20Or%20he%20as%20a%20Sikh%20is%20going%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20wear%20a%20Kada%20in%20India.%20Or%20a%20Sikh%20is%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20go%20to%20Gurdwara.%20That's%20what%20the%20fight%20is%20about%20and%20not%20just%20for%20him%2C%20for%20all%20religions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20might%20lead%20some%20to%20believe%20that%20Sikhs%20and%20other%20minority%20communities%20in%20India%20face%20significant%20religious%20discrimination.%20In%20reality%2C%20such%20issues%20have%20been%20rare%2C%20with%20the%20notable%20exception%20of%20the%201984%20anti-Sikh%20riots%2C%20which%20followed%20the%20assassination%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20Several%20Congress%20leaders%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20complicity%20in%20those%20riots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20received%20immediate%20support%20from%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20a%20militant%20Khalistan%20proponent%20and