EHuang%20revealed%20that%20her%20father%2C%20whose%20age%20has%20not%20been%20disclosed%2C%20experienced%20persistent%20pain%20following%20the%20treatment.%20''I%20never%20thought%20my%20dad%20would%20pass%20so%20quickly.%20He%20did%20not%20even%20get%20the%20chance%20to%20drive%20the%20new%20car%20we%20bought%20him%2C''%20stated%20his%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20incident%2C%20an%20official%20from%20the%20Yongkang%20Municipal%20Health%20Bureau%20stated%20on%20September%203%20that%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20is%20still%20being%20investigated%2C%20citing%20the%2013-day%20gap%20between%20the%20dental%20procedure%20and%20the%20man's%20death.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3EThree%20days%20later%2C%20a%C2%A0clinic%20staff%20member%20told%20%3Cem%3ESCMP%3C%2Fem%3E%20''We%20will%20not%20be%20responding%20to%20this%20matter%20now%20as%20it%20has%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20our%20lawyer.%20If%20there%20are%20any%20updates%2C%20we%20will%20issue%20a%20statement%3B%20however%2C%20the%20investigation%20is%20ongoing.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20Xiang%20Guolin%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Dental%20Medicine%20Centre%20at%20the%20Hospital%20of%20Universal%20Love%20in%20Wuhan%2C%20there%20are%20no%20established%20official%20guidelines%20for%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20teeth%20that%20can%20be%20extracted%20in%20a%20single%20procedure.%20However%2C%20in%20general%20practice%2C%20the%20limit%20is%20typically%20considered%20to%20be%20around%2010%20teeth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Extracting%2023%20teeth%20is%20quite%20a%20lot.%20It%20requires%20a%20clinic%20and%20dentist%20with%20sufficient%20qualifications%20and%20experience.%20It's%20also%20essential%20to%20consider%20the%20patient's%20physical%20capacity%20to%20handle%20such%20an%20extensive%20procedure%2C''%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20social%20media%20users%20expressed%20shock%20and%20disbelief%20upon%20learning%20about%20the%20case.%20One%20person%20questioned%20the%20decision%20to%20extract%2023%20teeth%20in%20a%20single%20day%2C%20sharing%20their%20own%20experience%20of%20being%20refused%20by%20a%20dentist%20when%20requesting%20the%20removal%20of%20two%20wisdom%20teeth%20simultaneously.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20user%20wrote%2C%20''I'm%20a%20dentist%2C%20and%20I%20never%20extract%20more%20than%20three%20teeth%20at%20one%20time%20unless%20they're%20very%20loose.%20The%20doctor%20must%20have%20lost%20his%20mind.%20It%20sounds%20more%20like%20a%20human%20experiment%20than%20a%20dental%20procedure.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726059600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fktfk2s4g_dentist_625x300_11_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-man-gets-23-teeth-extracted-and-12-implants-placed-in-one-day-dies-of-heart-attack-6541684%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20procedure%20involved%20extracting%2023%20teeth%20and%20inserting%2012%20implants%20in%20a%20single%20day%20using%20the%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20restoration%26quot%3B%20method.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-man-gets-23-teeth-extracted-and-12-implants-placed-in-one-day-dies-of-heart-attack-6541684%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kamala%20Harris%20emerges%20unscathed%20from%20debate%2C%20dancing%20around%20her%20flip-flops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726059396000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113263851%2Cimgsize-962810.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fkamala-harris-emerges-unscathed-from-debate-dancing-around-her-flip-flops%2Farticleshow%2