%20their%20dishes%20directly.%20This%20would%20help%20them%20become%20financially%20independent%20and%20turn%20their%20passion%20into%20a%20thriving%20business.%20For%20customers%2C%20it%20offers%20a%20way%20to%20enjoy%20the%20local%20delicacies%20they%20crave!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20in%202023%2C%20Tocco%20now%20has%20over%2016%20chefs%2C%20both%20men%20and%20women%2C%20mostly%20in%20their%2050s%2C%20whose%20dreams%20have%20been%20given%20wings%20through%20the%20platform!%20Starting%20with%20just%20Rs%205%2C000%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355942%2Forganic-masala-spices-in-coimbatore-tamil-nadu-iniya-organics-business-podis-health-mixes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebootstrapped%20business%20%3C%2Fa%3Eachieved%20a%20turnover%20of%20over%20Rs%201%20crore%20in%20the%20current%20year.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20Reshma%20is%20empowering%20those%20with%20a%20lifelong%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPacking%20childhood%20memories%20in%20a%20box%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReshma%2C%20an%20engineer%2C%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%20in%202012%20for%20work.%20She%20worked%20in%20healthcare%20startups%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20gaining%20first-hand%20experience%20in%20healthcare%20and%20health%20tech.%20Joining%20these%20startups%20from%20their%20infancy%2C%20she%20had%20a%20front-row%20understanding%20of%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20scale%20a%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusy%20with%20work%2C%20a%20huge%20portion%20of%20her%2020s%20was%20spent%20eating%20out%20or%20cooking%20for%20herself.%20She%20constantly%20craved%20a%20good%20home-cooked%20meal%2C%20just%20like%20the%20ones%20her%20mother%20used%20to%20make.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20missed%20my%20roots%20and%20the%20food%20I%20grew%20up%20eating.%20Every%20time%20I%20visited%20home%20in%20Kochi%2C%20I%20brought%20back%20staples%20like%20banana%20chips%2C%20pickles%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Epodi